Installing the moltbx version of MolProbity:

1. Run the configure.sh script. This will install cctbx_project and needed components in moltbx/sources:

    build list:
     annlib
     annlib_adaptbx
     boost
     cbflib
     ccp4io
     ccp4io_adaptbx
     cctbx_project
     chem_data
     lapack_fem
     probe
     reduce
     scons
     tntbx

and then will compile and configure in moltbx/build.

2. Run setup.sh to configure the webserver. Make sure that the machine's Apache configuration can point to the moltbx/public_html directory.
